OL,4,CMuseum Cardiff is not closing
OL,6,FA Welsh Government cabinet secretary
OL,7,Fhas insisted National Museum Cardiff
OL,8,Fwill not close after concerns were
OL,9,Fraised about its funding and the
OL,10,Fbuidling falling into disrepair.
OL,12,Fchief executive Jane Richardson spoke
OL,13,Fwith BBC Radio Wales' Sunday
OL,14,FSupplement programme, saying the
OL,15,Forganisation is facing a #4.5million
OL,16,Freduction in its budget, which is set
OL,17,Fby the Welsh Government.
