OL,6,FHeledd Fychan, Plaid Cymru MS for
OL,7,FSouth Wales Central, said: "What
OL,8,Fassessment has the cabinet secretary
OL,9,Fmade of National Museum Wales possibly
OL,10,Fclosing National Museum Cardiff due to
OL,11,Fdeteriorating conditions?"
OL,13,FMs Griffiths said: "My officials
OL,14,Fcontinue to work with () to develop a
OL,15,Fplan to address the urgent maintenance
OL,16,Fissues at our building in .
OL,18,F"I met with the chief executive
OL,19,Fyesterday (Tuesday) who assured me
OL,20,Fthere are no plans to close the museum.
