OL,6,F"However I fully appreciate the
OL,7,Fseriousness of the situation and the
OL,8,Fsignificant investment needed."
OL,10,FFollowing up on the initial question,
OL,11,FLabour MS Alun Davies said: "The
OL,12,Fpeople of Wales should never be put in
OL,13,Fa position where they're told they
OL,14,Fhave to choose between seeing a GP or
OL,15,Fa Van Gogh.
OL,17,F"Having access to our national
OL,18,Fcollection is important to who we are
OL,19,Fand not just us as a nation but also
OL,20,Fus as a family and as a community."
