OL,6,FThe question from Ms Fychan came after
OL,7,FFirst Minister 's comment at a press
OL,8,Fconference on Tuesday (April 16), in
OL,9,Fwhich he defended the cuts made to the
OL,10,Fculture sector.
OL,12,FHe said: "I would much rather we have
OL,13,Fthe money we require to deliver
OL,14,Fexcellent public services and to
OL,15,Fsupport the growth in the economy.
OL,16,FThat's what I want to be able to do
OL,17,Fnow and in the future.
OL,19,F"For me to have priorities now, we're
OL,20,Fgoing to have to make choices on what
OL,21,Fwe're going to do.
