OL,6,F"We're well past the point where being
OL,7,Fmore innovative gets you over the
OL,8,Fline. We're at a point where real
OL,9,Fchoices have to be made about what
OL,10,Fwe're not going to do.
OL,12,F"I'd like to see a future where the
OL,13,FNational Museum can do the work
OL,14,Frequired on the building and continues
OL,15,Fto provide an excellent service.
OL,17,F"That requires different choices about
OL,18,Fhow we grow the economy across Wales
OL,19,Fand how that wealth is shared fairly
OL,20,Facross the country.
